name: Molten Core
description:
I created this piece, stemming from a twitter post from Penny Farthing (https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/penny_farthing) about colour. I got to see a whole bunch of great artists, meet some new people and got some new followers. I appreciate being included in the conversation. 

Of the run of 35, and at the time of minting, all those that got tagged or participated in the conversation, and I that could find a xyz account for, will receive one, as a thank you for conversation.
